title.narrative: PNG Election Capacity Strengthening Support Programme

description.narrative: Support the Papua New Guinea Electoral Commission (PNGEC) to deliver the 2017 national election through technical support from the NZ Electoral Commission. Assistance includes the deployment of technical advisers, training and hosting observation visits to NZ by PNGEC officials, and build a database to recruit 35,000 temporary election workers.
